{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja monitor template for Spectra LS P6-S04 control-input execution validation and bounded closeout gating. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.21.1 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-21 #}

{# =========================
  P6-S04 Control-Input Execution Monitor (dry-run-first)
  Purpose: classify execution-lane readiness and closeout posture for `spectra_ls.execute_control_center_input`.
  Usage:
    1) Run one or more `spectra_ls.execute_control_center_input` calls (dry-run first).
    2) Paste/run this in Developer Tools -> Template.
    3) Capture output in checklist evidence block.
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target_primary = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_target_fallback = 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set primary_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_primary, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_primary, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set fallback_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set s_target = s_target_primary if primary_has_attrs else (s_target_fallback if fallback_has_attrs else s_target_primary) %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set unresolved = state_attr(s_target, 'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set mismatches = state_attr(s_target, 'mismatches') or [] %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set control_settings = write_controls.control_center_settings if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.control_center_settings is defined and write_controls.control_center_settings is mapping else {} %}
{% set last_attempt = write_controls.control_center_last_attempt if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.control_center_last_attempt is defined and write_controls.control_center_last_attempt is mapping else {} %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set unresolved_required = contract.unresolved_required if contract is mapping and contract.unresolved_required is defined else [] %}

{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set snapshot_fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{% set read_only_mode = control_settings.read_only_mode if control_settings is mapping and control_settings.read_only_mode is defined else true %}
{% set last_status = last_attempt.status if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.status is defined else 'never_attempted' %}
{% set last_reason = last_attempt.reason if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.reason is defined else 'n/a' %}
{% set last_mapped_action = last_attempt.mapped_action if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.mapped_action is defined else '' %}
{% set last_input_event = last_attempt.input_event if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.input_event is defined else '' %}
{% set last_dry_run = last_attempt.dry_run if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.dry_run is defined else none %}

{# --- Operator-confirmed P6 execution governance gates (set true/false before capture) --- #}
{% set p6_s03_active = true %}
{% set dry_run_first_posture = true %}
{% set read_only_enforcement_expected = true %}
{% set rollback_posture_documented = true %}

{% set runtime_baseline_gate_pass = authority_mode == 'legacy' and contract_valid and (missing_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved | length) == 0 and (mismatches | length) == 0 and snapshot_fresh %}
{% set execution_surface_gate_pass = last_status != 'never_attempted' %}
{% set dry_run_gate_pass = last_dry_run == true and last_status in ['dry_run_ok', 'blocked_read_only_mode', 'blocked_scene_unconfigured', 'blocked_unmapped_input', 'blocked_unknown_input_event'] %}
{% set read_only_gate_pass = (read_only_mode == true and read_only_enforcement_expected) or (read_only_mode == false) %}

{% set governance_gate_pass = p6_s03_active and dry_run_first_posture and rollback_posture_documented %}

{% set gate_pass_count = (1 if runtime_baseline_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if execution_surface_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if dry_run_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if read_only_gate_pass else 0)
  + (1 if governance_gate_pass else 0) %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if not runtime_baseline_gate_pass or not execution_surface_gate_pass %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif not dry_run_gate_pass or not read_only_gate_pass or not governance_gate_pass %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

{% set p6_readiness = 'NOT_READY' %}
{% if status == 'PASS' and gate_pass_count == 5 %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'READY' %}
{% elif status == 'FAIL' %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'BLOCKED' %}
{% else %}
  {% set p6_readiness = 'CAUTION' %}
{% endif %}

### P6-S04 Control-Input Execution Monitor (`spectra_ls`)
- Status: **{{ status }}**
- P6-S04 readiness: **{{ p6_readiness }}**
- Gate score: **{{ gate_pass_count }}/5**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Runtime + execution gates (live)
- Runtime baseline gate (legacy + clean contract/parity + fresh): **{{ runtime_baseline_gate_pass }}**
- Execution surface gate (at least one attempt captured): **{{ execution_surface_gate_pass }}**
- Dry-run-first gate: **{{ dry_run_gate_pass }}**
- Read-only enforcement gate: **{{ read_only_gate_pass }}**
- Governance gate (P6-S03 active + dry-run/rollback posture): **{{ governance_gate_pass }}**

### Execution snapshot
- `authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `route_trace.decision`: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `read_only_mode`: **{{ read_only_mode }}**
- `last_attempt.status`: **{{ last_status }}**
- `last_attempt.input_event`: **{{ last_input_event if last_input_event != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_attempt.mapped_action`: **{{ last_mapped_action if last_mapped_action != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_attempt.dry_run`: **{{ last_dry_run if last_dry_run is not none else 'n/a' }}**
- `last_attempt.reason`: **{{ last_reason }}**
- `contract_validation.missing_required`: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- `contract_validation.unresolved_required`: **{{ unresolved_required | length }}**
- `unresolved_sources`: **{{ unresolved | length }}**
- `mismatches`: **{{ mismatches | length }}**
- Freshness (`captured_at<=300s`): **{{ snapshot_fresh }}** (age_s={{ (age_s | round(1)) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

### Quick interpretation
{% if p6_readiness == 'READY' %}
- P6-S04 execution lane is healthy for bounded validation evidence and closeout tracking.
{% elif p6_readiness == 'CAUTION' %}
- P6-S04 is partially healthy; resolve dry-run/read-only/governance gaps before closeout.
{% elif p6_readiness == 'BLOCKED' %}
- P6-S04 is blocked by baseline or execution-surface failure; resolve before proceeding.
{% else %}
- P6-S04 readiness is not established yet; gather missing evidence and re-run.
{% endif %}

### Suggested refresh actions
- Run `spectra_ls.execute_control_center_input` in dry-run mode for one mapped input event.
- Keep `authority_mode=legacy` baseline unless an explicitly approved bounded slice changes ownership.
- Attach this output to `p6_s04_control_input_execution_checklist.md` evidence record.
